</style><p>白银诺埃尔宣布，她将暂停直播活动直至 9 月 13 日。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"> https://twitter.com/shiroganenoel/status/1697444163716100570?t=9j-Q3ATfHGdey0MNilO1Uw&amp;s=19</div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCdyqAaZDKHXg4Ahi7VENThQ" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">诺埃尔 Ch. Shirogane</a><a href="https://twitter.com/shiroganenoel">诺埃尔<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2694.png" alt="⚔" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> Hololive 第 3 代</a>/ <a href="https://hololive.hololivepro.com/talents/shirogane-noel/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="">Shirogane Noel</a></p> <cite>YouTube / X（推特）/ Hololive Production</cite></blockquote><p> （ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“No.2（暂定）”</em> /虚拟元宇宙VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-en wp-block-embed-p-2-y-en"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="NmU9hWiomJ"> <a href="https://en.p2y.jp/vtuber-shiragane-noel-encountered-a-problem-logging-in-to-her-official-x-twitter-account/">VTuber Shiragane Noel 在登录其官方 X (Twitter) 帐户时遇到问题</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber Shiragane Noel 在登录她的官方 X (Twitter) 帐户时遇到问题” — P2y.EN" src="https://en.p2y.jp/vtuber-shiragane-noel-encountered-a-problem-logging-in-to-her-official-x-twitter-account/embed/#?secret=8dCsxIyyKL#?secret=NmU9hWiomJ" data-secret="NmU9hWiomJ" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-shiragane-noel-encountered-a-problem-logging-in-to-her-official-x-twitter-account/">VTuber Shirogane Noel X (Twitter) 无法登录官方账号的问题</a>首先出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/vtuber-shiragane-noel-enco