ive 2代成员（Aqua Minato、Shion Shisaki、Subaru Ozora、Ayame Hyakki、Choco Yuzuki）全部5名订阅者都达到了100万，我们已经实现了这一里程碑。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>人才名称</td><td>注册人数（较1个月前增减）</td></tr><tr><td>治愈月亮巧克力</td><td>100 万人（+13,000 人）</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">截至2023年9月7日11:00 </figcaption></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-4-3 wp-has-aspect-ratio"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><div class="youtube"><iframe title="【仅上】恶魔的挑战！ 100万人耐力！ ！ ！ ！ [hololive/柚木巧克力]" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/noDoyGAyIYM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></div></div></figure><p></p><div class="cqxfe64fb2ba23e424" ><script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-3186024119059876"
