</style><p>另外，过去曾与楠木诗织共同主演过麻将发行，据说也与麻将界有渊源的千波同外（独立/二十三寺未来军堂所属艺人）。龙滨月的推特（帖子）：“<em>我感觉我已经等了很长时间了。 <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f338.png" alt="🌟" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></em> 》被转发（转发），并且也确认了龙滨先生正在回复独贝女士。</p><p>除此之外 ” <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f338.png" alt="🌟" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> ” 标记也是楠木诗织的“推荐标记”，所以Poison先生有可能认为龙滨老师就是楠木诗织先生。</p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/0_Doku_0/status/1698607710965747899" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc-uiPVuc0_jUFONldmO_UUsUD5Q_SUxN7_LGYbKX92A4-7SEQPo-og-PwO122pyLaS1_uPOyzyI-TjCqpMAY9fDgCWSnd0Iyj1pQqMrejviwVCdNzNRYN5GzPD_mLOyu6GfEIGLoRa_FKyH4pXhYpY9=w1097-h1709-s-no" alt=""/></a></figure><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"> <a href="https://twitter.com/yue_fsp/status/1698614890142068817" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener"><img decoding="async" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/pw/AIL4fc9ZJxoW0YrL4x47cxFjOuzylFfPaa6rWg_kr1VihYg2v1c2bdwanC50sN7B-h1FU3MqqU4-yQa7r7NeDIwaYI_tCqLWf7GFbJrJH_j9dveZp0ofjLySdFFyT7ix6lZ_dGVUtxBf7rH7NwJ9lAcM9EL4=w1097-h1798-s-no" alt=""/></a></figure><p>上述信息并非可以100%确定Ryugahama先生就是Sakura Kusunoki先生的信息。目前，属于不确定谣言范围，请不要做出给艺人本人或经纪公司带来麻烦或诽谤的行为。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="pHNLHb15An"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-first-stage-production-announces-commencement-of-legal-action-against-slander-etc/">VTuber办公室FIRST STAGE PRODUCTION宣布开始针对诽谤等采取法律行动。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“VTuber办公室FIRST STAGE PRODUCTION宣布开始针对诽谤采取法律行动” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-agency-first-stage-production-announces-com